name: Travelers Demise
description:
The solar sail of a ship stands alone after the crash. Stranded from its hull and crew which fell into a ravine on this icy planet.

The glow from the wreckage illuminates the icy mountainside.
Soon it will all freeze over
Frozen in time
Where the sail will stand for thousands of years, untouched. Until the next poor crew has the misfortune of becoming stranded on this desolate world.

And becomes frozen in time.
